name: My Babies
description:
My Babies! The newest addition to the My Baby Creations family.  All babies are made from 100% usuable baby products.  Once mommy or daddy takes the baby apart, they have a days' worth of useful baby items to pack in a to go bag, send to grandma's or simply put away in the nursery.

Considering all you get with this gift item, the price is a complete bargain! It's even the perfect gift to give to a godmother-to-be, grandm-to-be or an auntie.  

Size notes - you can specify Newborn (0 - 3 months), Infant (3 - 6 months), Crawler (6 - 9 months), 1st Birthday (12 - 18 months)

Each "My Newborn" Contains:
- wash cloth face (filled with diapers)
- outfit (filled with 20 - 30 diapers)
- hat
- pacifier (teething toy for 1st Birthday)
- bib
- mittens (so baby doesn't scratch her face)
- slippers, shoes or socks
- baby bottle (training cup for 1st Birthday)
  
*Optional accesories like toys, additional clothing, blanket, burp cloths, etc available at additional cost.

Style Notes: 
- Duckie or Unisex (clothing is nuetral for boy or girl),
- Sweet Baby Girl/Boy (traditional baby clothing like a sleeper or sweet two-piece outfit)
- Dressed Like a Big Girl/Boy (outfit is like a suit, dress, jeans, sweater vest, etc that makes the baby look like their going out or ready for a special picture)
- 1st Birthday (comes in Dressed Like a Big Girl/Boy style only)

name: My Baby Baskets
description:
A different take on the diaper cake approach.

These themed and decorated baskets are filled with lots of baby goodies and I can customize to your liking, just like with the diaper cake.

WHEN ORDERING 
- specify how much you want to spend 
- theme (can be very specific like jungle theme above or simple like boy or unisex)
- any must INCLUDE or EXCLUDE items (examples: no bottles, include onsies with days of the week, etc)


As Shown ($80):
- 40 diapers
- 3 coordinating All-Star outfits
- shoes
- socks (4 pair)
- burp cloths (6)
- mittens (4 pair)
- wash cloths (6)
- hats (5)

name: My Diaper Cakes
description:
The classic Diaper Cake with My special touches.  These cakes can range in price from $25 - 120.00 depending on the size and items you'd like to include.  

My Diaper Cakes can be themed by color, character, sex of the baby, sports, girlie themes, etc.  You want it, I can do it - even a jungle themed cake complete with leopard, zebra and cheetah print clothing and goodies for the baby girl.

WHEN ORDERING 
- specify how much you want to spend 
- theme (can be very specific like jungle theme above or simple like boy or unisex)
- any must INCLUDE or EXCLUDE items (examples: no bottles, include onsies with days of the week, etc)

Diaper Cake As Shown ($120)
- 100 diapers
- 25 bottles of varying sizes
- toys
- bottle brushes
- wash cloths
- burp cloths
- pacifiers
- nail clippers
- socks
- bottle & nipple brushes
- receiving blankets
- toys
- pacifier clip
- onsies
- all on top of a scapbook
